Posts.Title: Would you mind sharing your age at time of diagnosis? ByFaith Gussy

Posts.Content: BDawk wrote: Recovering from BMX with TE expanders on 8/12. I am due for my 1st fill this coming Thursday 9/3. What is it like? Does it hurt? The pain was becoming manageable -- that is until I has my drains removed last Thursday 8/27. It was horrible, but the next day.... I wanted to report a hit and run of the truck that ran me over. Felt like I regressed. As the day wears on I feel worse..barely any sleep. Just wanted to know what I'm facing now that I'm at the point of getting the fills. Any suggestions, comments etc would totally rock! Thanks! Dx 7/2015, DCIS, Right, Stage 0, 0/4 nodes, ER+/PR- Log in to post a reply
